    <item>
      <title>杰富瑞：裕信银行可能不会在 7 月前竞购德国商业银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/unicredit-may-not-bid-for-commerzbank-before-july-jefferies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰富瑞金融集团 (Jefferies Financial Group Inc.) 分析师表示，意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 应推迟到明年下半年再对德国商业银行 (Commerzbank AG) 发出收购要约，以避免触发强制现金报价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/unicredit-may-not-bid-for-commerzbank-before-july-jefferies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 14:41:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
